name: PHP Dorset User Group
body: ### Welcome to PHP Dorset user group So, we're here and starting up in November 2013. Follow us on twitter to find out when the first meet up is. If you're interested in speaking then please get in touch:- IRC: #phpdorset on freenode.net Twitter: https://twitter.com/phpdorset Forum: https://moot.it/phpdorset
